summary: Faendal have a lot of modifications.
descriptionHtml:
I have a better version of Faendal.

that  are the  modifications:

* new face
* new hair
* Faendal have lvl 20 as initial lvl and are auto-level and go to lvl 255
* combat style changed to \'\'csforsworm beseker low\'\'( the same style of Jenassa)
* he carry and uses Daedric arrows
* he is re-spawn
* he not turn over against  you if you commit a crime or kill anyone (that\'s my main point that i hate the original)
* Mood : Neutral (original : Disgusted)
* Assistance - Friends and Allies
* He uses 2 Ebony Daggers (original are only 1 iron dagger)

I hope you like it.
I tested and works great. Soon i will make other modifications to Faendal looks like LOTR Legolas.


Have fun !


Recommended mods :

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26493 by Dart98Rock
